{"tid":2366432,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"靜電 我今次真係屌你老母","createTime":"2021-01-14T13:04:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T13:45:13.000Z","uid":134270,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e055bb4dd3dedc35c08903a4f4ff0627317252eb","tid":2366432,"uid":134270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T13:04:15.000Z","msg":"話說我一直都好中意我女神 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日終於約到佢出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同佢食飯再送左幾貴嘅袋比佢<br />\n<br />\n個刻佢個樣話我知 佢一定100%係中意我！！<br />\n<br />\n跟住同佢去左觀塘海濱傾下計談下心<br />\n<br />\n我見氣氛幾好 我望住佢 同佢表左白<br />\n<br />\n佢個樣似係諗緊 點樣回應應承我<br />\n<br />\n我捉緊呢個機會 順勢拖起佢隻手<br />\n<br />\n點知係我掂到佢嘅一刻 <br />\n<br />\n有靜電啊屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n我地縮左一縮 呢個時候我當然要扮型<br />\n<br />\n咪再拖埋去 顯露我天不怕 地不怕嘅性格<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候 佢推開我 仲話好痛啊 <br />\n<br />\n話呢件事一定係個天嘅安排<br />\n<br />\n跟住佢轉身就走左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我咩都做唔到<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>天啊 點解要咁作弄我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"39f7abbf953edfa3cbbc05a71458df0191a9b0d8","tid":2366432,"uid":229633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T13:05:11.000Z","msg":"佢推開我 仲話好痛啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa749d03ca32222f04b1c72765dd3e8c32c901f4","tid":2366432,"uid":206594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T13:06:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A1HKswA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA1HKswA.gif&h=95b81aec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38a8101960b388b583b8cc0e5c54328d22973f98","tid":2366432,"uid":134270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"qu